               SMB clients, such as Windows 95/98, Windows NT, Windows
               for Workgroups or LanManager. The configuration file
               for this daemon is described in _s_m_b._c_o_n_f

          nnnnmmmmbbbbdddd The nnnnmmmmbbbbdddd daemon provides NetBIOS nameserving and
               browsing support. The configuration file for this
               daemon is described in _s_m_b._c_o_n_f

